text: Nikolay Chuchalov (13 August 1932 - 5 May 2011) was a Soviet wrestler. He competed in the men's Greco-Roman middleweight at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1932 births Category:2011 deaths Category:Soviet male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of the Soviet Union Category:Wrestlers at the 1960 Summer Olympics
